# FILE: halabStore/productDetail/productDetail.desc
# ROLE: Technical Spec-Sheet & Transaction Terminal
# ROUTE: /store/product/:id
# ACCOUNT: All account types can view and purchase
# THEME: Dark · data-heavy · industrial precision

## 1. HERO SPLIT (60/40)
- LEFT (IMAGE GALLERY):
  - Main image: large · rounded-2xl · bg-[#0F1828] · hover zoom
  - Thumbnail strip: 4 small images below · active has border-[#6366F1]
- RIGHT (BUY BOX):
  - TITLE: text-2xl font-bold text-[#F1F5F9]
  - PRODUCT ID: "#HS-102" — text-[#4A5D78] monospace text-sm
  - STATUS: [✅ متوفر حالياً] emerald · [⏳ قيد التأمين] amber
  - SOURCE BADGE: 🏠 منصة (teal) or 🤝 وسيط (amber) + vendor name if business account
  - SAVINGS METER: "وفّرت X SYP عبر HalabUnver" — emerald text
  - PRICE: gradient-text large · original price strikethrough gray
  - PRIMARY CTA: [💳 حجز وإتمام الدفع] → 2-hour reservation lock
  - SECONDARY: [💬 تواصل عبر واتساب]

## 2. LOGISTICS BENTO (Admin/Vendor Controlled)
- SOURCE NOTE:
  - 🏠 منصة: "مملوك للمنصة — في مستودعاتنا المحلية"
  - 🤝 وسيط: "تأمين خارجي — فُحص بالكامل من HalabUnver"
- PICKUP LOCATION: admin/vendor text (e.g., "بوابة كلية الهندسة")
- DELIVERY TIMELINE: "فوري" or "3-5 أيام عمل"
- WARRANTY BOX: "3 أيام استرداد في حالة عطل الجهاز"

## 3. TECHNICAL DNA (Spec Sheet)
- MONOSPACE TABLE: border · rounded-xl · alternating row bg
  - Columns: المعيار · القيمة (CPU · RAM · Battery · Weight etc.)
- STAFF NOTE: rich-text visible if admin/vendor added notes
- DATASHEET: [📄 تحميل المواصفات الرسمية (PDF)]

## 4. ADMIN/VENDOR OVERRIDE (Sticky)
- accountType === 'admin': floating [✏️ تعديل المنتج] button → /admin/inventory/:id
- businessType === 'vendor' (product owner): floating [✏️ تعديل] button → /business/products/:id

## 5. RELATED PRODUCTS
- 4-card horizontal scroll with same card style as /store catalog
